Below is a simplified example of how the Bright Data scraper was integrated via the HTTP Request node in n8n to fetch real-time medicine prices:


{
  "url": "https://collector.brightdata.com/api/collector/dataset/medicine_prices",
  "method": "POST",
  "headers": {
    "Authorization": "Bearer YOUR_BRIGHTDATA_API_KEY",
    "Content-Type": "application/json"
  },
  "body": {
    "query": "paracetamol 500mg price",
    "location": "USA"
  }
}

The response from Bright Data was parsed and used to update a Google Sheet with structured drug pricing data.
